import Vue from 'vue'
import Router from 'vue-router'
import Home from './components/tabbar/Home.vue'
import register from './components/tabbar/register.vue'
import login from './components/tabbar/login.vue'
import signout from './components/tabbar/sigout.vue'

import shoplist from './components/tabbar/shoplist.vue'

import NewsList from './components/home/NewsList.vue'
import NewsInfo from './components/home/NewsInfo.vue'
import GoodsList from './components/goods/GoodsList.vue'
import GoodsInfo from './components/goods/GoodsInfo.vue'
Vue.use(Router)

export default new Router({
  routes: [
    {path:'/',redirect:"/Home"},   //用户访问/ 重新定位/Home 
    {path:'/Home',component:Home},
    {path:'/NewsList',component:NewsList},
    {path:'/NewsInfo/:id',component:NewsInfo},
    {path:'/GoodsList',component:GoodsList},
    {path:'/GoodsInfo/:id',component:GoodsInfo},
    {path:'/register',component:register},
    {path:'/login',component:login},
    {path:'/sigout',component:sigout},
    {path:'/shoplist',component:shoplist},
  ]
})
